700694f.title: Bronx: Bussing Avenue - Baychester Avenue
700694f.text:
Bussing Ave., east from but not including Baychester Ave., as it makes
a sharp bend southward and becomes Bussing Place for the length of one
block. This part of the avenue is no longer in existence and is part
of block No. 5023. The 2-story houses in the background face on Wilder
Ave.
June 6, 1928.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
